<li><a href="http://www.iep.utm.edu/c/cog-rel.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.iep.utm.edu/c/cog-rel.htm" rel="nofollow">Internet Encyclopedia of Philosophy on Cognitive Relativism</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.friesian.com/relative.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.friesian.com/relative.htm" rel="nofollow">The Friesian School on Relativism</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.newadvent.org/cathen/12731d.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.newadvent.org/cathen/12731d.htm" rel="nofollow">The Catholic Encyclopedia</a></li>
<li><a href="http://ndpr.nd.edu/review.cfm?id=8364" class="external text" title="http://ndpr.nd.edu/review.cfm?id=8364" rel="nofollow">Harvey Siegel reviews</a> <a href="/wiki/Paul_Boghossian" title="Paul Boghossian">Paul Boghossian</a>'s <i>Fear of Knowledge</i></li>
</ul>
